statements: SELECT * FROM user_interactions;
SELECT user_id, interaction_type FROM user_interactions WHERE interaction_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT COUNT(interaction_id) FROM user_interactions WHERE interaction_type = 'click';
SELECT user_id, AVG(response_time) AS avg_response_time FROM user_interactions GROUP BY user_id;
SELECT interaction_id, interaction_type FROM user_interactions ORDER BY interaction_date DESC;
SELECT user_id, interaction_type FROM user_interactions WHERE user_id = 100 ORDER BY interaction_date DESC;
SELECT interaction_id, user_id, interaction_type, interaction_date FROM user_interactions WHERE interaction_type = 'click' ORDER BY interaction_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM user_interactions WHERE interaction_type IN ('click', 'hover') AND response_time > 0 ORDER BY user_id ASC, interaction_date DESC;
SELECT MAX(response_time) AS max_response_time, MIN(response_time) AS min_response_time FROM user_interactions;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_interactions FROM user_interactions GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 2 ORDER BY total_interactions DESC;
SELECT * FROM user_interactions WHERE user_id = 123
SELECT user_id, interaction_date, interaction_type FROM user_interactions WHERE interaction_date = '2022-01-15' ORDER BY interaction_time DESC
SELECT user_id, interaction_type, response_time_ms FROM user_interactions WHERE interaction_type = 'click' ORDER BY user_id ASC, interaction_time ASC
SELECT user_id, interaction_date, interaction_time, response_score FROM automated_responses WHERE response_score > 0.8 ORDER BY response_score DESC, user_id ASC
SELECT user_id, interaction_type, response_time_ms FROM user_interactions WHERE response_time_ms IS NOT NULL
SELECT user_id, MAX(response_time_ms) AS max_response_time FROM user_interactions GROUP BY user_id ORDER BY max_response_time DESC;
SELECT interaction_type, COUNT(*) AS interaction_count FROM user_interactions GROUP BY interaction_type HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
SELECT u.user_id, u.interaction_date, a.response_message FROM user_interactions u INNER JOIN automated_responses a ON u.user_id = a.user_id ORDER BY u.interaction_date DESC;
SELECT user_id, AVG(response_score) AS avg_response_score FROM automated_responses GROUP BY user_id HAVING AVG(response_score) > 3.5 ORDER BY user_id;
SELECT user_id, interaction_time FROM user_interactions UNION SELECT user_id, interaction_time FROM automated_responses ORDER BY user_id, interaction_time DESC;

SELECT user_id, interaction_type FROM interactions ORDER BY interaction_timestamp DESC;

SELECT user_id, interaction_timestamp, interaction_type, response_time FROM interactions ORDER BY interaction_timestamp DESC;
